    "title": "Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates is Hiring: Full Stack Developer (Principal)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Full Stack Developer to strengthen our Indore-based team.\n\nAbout Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates:\nNewgen Software Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Newgen Software Asia Pacific Associates!",
